<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="astonished-adj">astonished <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'stɒnɪʃt/    美 /ə'stɑːnɪʃt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>感到大为惊讶的</strong></h4>
<p>very surprised (amazed)：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I was astonished to see him here. 
在这儿见到他，我很惊讶。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I am astonished that he didn’t come. 
他没有来，我感到很惊讶。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You look <strong>astonished at</strong> / <strong>by</strong> the news.
你看上去对这个消息感到很惊讶。</p></div></div>